			<div id="" class="blx blxPnewsletterpromo2 blxM915  blox4_html  blxC11803">   <div class="promo freeform">
   <div class="hed hed-flex">IT Careers Survey</div>
     <div class="desc">Take our 10-minute survey and share your plans and predictions for the future of the IT profession. The results will be published in our <strong>IT Careers 2016</strong> special report.</div>
     <a class="call-to-action" href="https://response.questback.com/idg/careers16/" target="_blank">Take the survey now!</a>
